These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, bus, motorbike
1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
2. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
3. the person driving the train is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | motorbike | train | subway | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, woodworking, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | fishing | board-games | gardening | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, journalist, designer, nurse
1. the journalist is on the right of the designer##1
2. the journalist is on the far left or far right##3
3. the teacher is the teacher##1
4. the teacher is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | nurse | teacher | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
