 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, fantasy, adventure, zombie
1. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | fantasy | zombie | satire |

