3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | reading | hiking | woodworking |

