2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | skateboard | taxi | van |

